  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If doctors could do things like this, Mengele.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, when I wrote a poem, which I'm going to share, is, 'I know you by the way you treat me, and by the way you make me feel inside.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Those things tell me a lot about you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Those things, my friend, you cannot hide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's not your color, your race, your religion, or occupation that tells me who you are.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's your deeds of kindness or of cruelty that manifests best who you are.' So that's the only criteria.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's the only criteria by which I know people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Nowadays, I have people who are black and friends who are black and white and Gentile and Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't-- this is secondary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I-- when someone tells me, I have a degree, you don't impress me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I'm rich.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You don't impress me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But your actions, your actions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I realize this is important.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This is the values observed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And under those conditions, we lived constantly, and hanging, and beating, and, and frustration, and constantly living in constant terror and fear for your life, and this constantly starving.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For, for all those years, I was starved, tortured, and still wanted to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And under those conditions, till 1942-- from 1942 to 1945, I lived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then one morning we got up, and there was no appell, no counting, anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were taken on the death march.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
